  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate effectiveness of Dasatinib as the first line therapy
      for patients with newly diagnosed chronic myeloid leukemia in chronic phase in Japan.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
